System overview
Title: Surge Hiring Toolkit — Hybrid Hub Architecture

Core idea:

Hub 1: Recruiting & Security Hub

Focus: “Getting people in the door”

Combines: Pipeline Tracker, Interview Scorecard, e-QIP Manager, Recruiting Dashboard, Recruiting Checklist

Hub 2: Operations & Employee Hub

Focus: “Managing people once they’re here”

Combines: Master Employee Tracker, Staffing Dashboard, Retention Tracker, Risk Register, RACI, QA Scores, Checklists, Alerts, Change Log

Support documents (4 core docs):

Surge Playbook (Slide Deck): Leadership briefing and surge strategy.

Operations Guide (Word Doc): Master guide, activation protocol, QA monitoring plan, supervisor quick reference, daily standup agenda.

New Hire Kit (Word Doc): Day One packet + activation notice.

After-Action Report (Word Doc): Close-out and lessons learned.

Why the hybrid model works:

Natural split: Recruiting/Security vs. Operations/Employee lifecycle.

Clean handoff: Candidate → Employee = Hub 1 → Hub 2.

Version control sanity: 2 main spreadsheets instead of 1 mega-file.

Automation-friendly: Each hub uses formulas, dropdowns, and conditional formatting to drive dashboards and alerts—no macros, no VBA.
